Answer the pending clarification question Leadbay raised after a refine_prompt. The answer is stored as the new `user_prompt` and triggers regeneration. Pass `option_id` (preferred — pick from the offered options) or `text_answer` (free-text). Admin-only.

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} after leadbay_refine_prompt returns `status='clarification_pending'`.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} to set a brand-new prompt — use leadbay_refine_prompt.

{{include:headers/verification-required-if-write}}
